118
00:08:59,370 --> 00:08:59,790
Idiote !

119
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:01,080
Ne sors pas tout de suite !

120
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:05,500
Quoi, c'est bon, c'est fi...

121
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:11,000
Liz !

122
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:20,560
Non ! Non !

123
00:09:22,310 --> 00:09:23,600
Liz ! Accroche-toi !

124
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:42,200
